value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Using a CDN is the final step to improve your website's performances. I choose "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"http://cloudflare.com"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Cloudflare"}]},{"type":"text","value":" which offers a great free plan, enough for our needs. You just have to create an account, follow the add-a-site steps, redirect your domain's DNS and here you are !"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Don't forget to set a Browser Cache Expiration of 8 days or more."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"gimg","properties":{"alt":"Cloudflare cache setting","src":"cloudflare-cache.jpg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The bonus of using Cloudflare is the HTTPS options. Even if, like me, you host your code on a gh-pages, "},{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"you can enable SSL encryption"}]},{"type":"text","value":" between your users and Github. It is pretty interesting knowing that Google is more and more focused on encryption for each result."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"gimg","properties":{"alt":"Cloudflare cache setting","src":"cloudflare-ssl.jpg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Before relaunching all my magic analysis tools, I have to wait 24 hours to see the first CDN effects. Finally, my site takes 2.2s to be fully loaded and PageSpeed gave me a "},{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":